\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 As for any staff object, rests may have text underlay associated with them (see \b Verses\b0 ).\par
